<i>adverb</i>: 발랑 [발랑], 발라당 [발라당] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>발랑 [발랑]</dt><br>
<dd>1. on one's back</dd><br>
<dd>팔과 다리를 활짝 벌려 뒤로 가볍게 넘어지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one falling down backward with his/her arms and legs stretched fully.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cheekily</dd><br>
<dd>순박하거나 순수하지 않고 되바라진 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one being cheeky, not being pure or innocent.</dd><br>
<dd>3. with inside out</dd><br>
<dd>안과 밖이 훌쩍 뒤집히는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing something being turned inside out.</dd><br>
<dt>발라당 [발라당]</dt><br>
<dd>1. on one's back</dd><br>
<dd>팔과 다리를 활짝 벌려 뒤로 가볍게 넘어지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one falling down backward with his/her arms and legs stretched fully.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cheekily</dd><br>
<dd>순박하거나 순수하지 않고 되바라진 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one being cheeky, not being pure or innocent.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>